title: Galatasaray Themed Watch Face
summary: Galatasaray FC themed Watch Face for your Android Wear device
description: Galatasaray FC themed Watch Face for your Android Wear device. Please let us know if you are having any issues with the watch face. After installing you may need to re-sync all the apps from the Android Wear application for the watch face to show up on your watch.
descriptionHTML:
Galatasaray FC themed Watch Face for your Android Wear device.
Please let us know if you are having any issues with the watch face.
After installing you may need to re-sync all the apps from the Android Wear application for the watch face to show up on your watch.
comments: Cool app Well designed for free watch App . I recommend for everyone.
